<note n="0286001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0286001">「學地認定」，參照提舍尼三。</note>
<note n="0291002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0291002">「三輪」，出大品第一大犍度。</note>
<note n="0292003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0292003">「戲笑」，原本 ujjhaggikāya，依暹羅本 ujjagghikāya 譯之。</note>
<note n="0295004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0295004">「施食者」，本節之施食者是婦女。</note>
<note n="0307005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0307005">「眼向地」，原本 ukkhittacittā，依暹羅本 okkhittukkhitta 譯之。</note>
<note n="0307006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0307006">以下否定辭不一一譯出。</note>
<note n="0311007" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0311007">「捲」，原本 uppajji，依暹羅本 ubbhuji 譯之。</note>
<note n="0311008" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0311008">「留」，原本 sethena，依暹羅本 sesakaṁ 譯之。</note>
<note n="0312009" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0312009">「污則力淨之」，原本 uklāpaṁ su sodheyya，依暹羅本 uklāp' ussahaṁ sodheyyaṁ 譯之。</note>
<note n="0313010" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0313010">「不成」，原本 na……sāve，依暹羅本 na……bhave 譯之。</note>
</p>
